、長相廝守<br />\n另外：<br />\n假使世界原來不像你預期、離遊記、忘記有時、UWILC、Common Sense 都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n不得不讚AGA，night without you、吃定我、孤雛（係咪今年？） 全部都高質得嚟無重複</blockquote><br />\ncome with me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17年kary雖然低產但好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同alexfung幾有火花<br />\n<br />\n靈感床 <br />\nact鵝act餓~ 好洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我鍾意說再見了吧多啲<br />\n<br />\n長相廝守 <br />\n雖然overrated, 但首歌唔差<br />\n作隻hit得起嘅k歌其實唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n方皓玟 17年嘅歌 我反而鍾意let's say<br />\n王雙駿17年造啲歌幾啱我口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n王菀之 17年又多產又首首高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連兩首翻唱都好精彩<br />\n唔知點解好似硬係冇乜反應咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\naga 17年啲歌真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (孤雛係16年派)<br />\n如果吃定我去得再盡少少就正<br />\nremix版嘅3am都造得好好<br />\nbtw, 新歌聽咗未？無期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a14ce88c4b7f5501d348936f6db80633e211d3","tid":523793,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:04:52.000Z","msg":"一晃眼<br />\n你帶著我的青春離去"},{"pid":"8ca14a0176c94a6d6f2f74654b6e3c1a8d6c823b","tid":523793,"uid":159140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"衛蘭 - I Don&rsquo;t Know I Don&rsquo;t Care<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UGXfuU56gpU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUGXfuU56gpU&d=rCHP49TNAiE945zI%2FoVsG2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b60c8903\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UGXfuU56gpU</a>"},{"pid":"fe544b859d00457b66e6bbbdaa3866fec2a3d6c3","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Serrini <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始淨係聽過兩首單曲 只係覺得幾過癮<br />\n但聽埋隻碟真係不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好鍾意佢有時大癲大廢 有時又文奏奏咁<br />\n17隻歌 好多唔同曲風都carry都好好<br />\n重點係咁多首歌又好連貫，成隻碟個concept present得好好<br />\n誠意推介大家聽依隻碟 don't text him<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 佢同楊彤嗰個組合gtb 啲歌都好正 勁bitchy勁抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c2005be371eed64ec42b4fb7bf3c2d7cce8200","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一晃眼</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>衛蘭 - I Don&rsquo;t Know I Don&rsquo;t Care<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UGXfuU56gpU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUGXfuU56gpU&d=rCHP49TNAiE945zI%2FoVsG2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b60c8903\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UGXfuU56gpU</a></blockquote><br />\n衛蘭唱咩都好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依兩年啲歌 我都聽得幾多嘅 因為把聲真係好吸引，<br />\n但有時硬係覺得差緊啲 差緊啲，總係覺得衛蘭應該可以做得更加好<br />\n我覺得佢音樂上應該要快啲有返個鮮明啲嘅character同清晰啲嘅方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 隻國語碟都係good try來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770bc0b1f05a7e0e23f958a5d680db94cbd26b83","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n你帶著我的青春離去</blockquote><br />\n覺得依首同妒忌心 都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但反而 原來只因深愛着 同 安全感 反應好啲&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8af9632b891a2e711271bd83d9258e88a3bc42","tid":523793,"uid":157755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"大概大概 帶著骨灰去旅行"},{"pid":"65891c4b488ef80351b35c89ee41dbd36d6160df","tid":523793,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T01:29:41.000Z","msg":"j arie首無神論都幾躍進"},{"pid":"97b32ec682d636c1c021c04a30cc536e0ae7986a","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大概大概 帶著骨灰去旅行</blockquote><br />\n大概大概 首歌幾好聽<br />\n不過暫時未夠令人好記得徐加晴依個人<br />\n佢同余香凝 林若盈 黃意雅 幾位新人都係識別度唔夠高<br />\n<br />\n帶着骨灰去旅行 立立感動之作<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢近年間中都有佳作，<br />\n但我成日嫌佢把聲好似略為悶/平"},{"pid":"65c0be80435a772cb5c5b7d7380e45b60e816c5e","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>j arie首無神論都幾躍進</blockquote><br />\n都係嘅 尤其對上嗰首係fantasy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首歌個過寫得幾好，<br />\n但我始終喜歡佢第一隻碟啲歌多啲"},{"pid":"0100b7cdb715263d229271242906aab3695abfb2","tid":523793,"uid":50676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"神奇之旅都幾好聽"},{"pid":"c53c998c2180cd373c39f7560c08e24def1a28b5","tid":523793,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e145ad0eac0f699794bb49c398e1591a8254d9f","tid":523793,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"依家個堆新秀真係無乜人識 唔入呢個POST都唔知有咩歌 廣東歌依家係唔係冇老細肯宣傳 除左上CCTVB個堆/電台 唔睇CCTVB同電台等同唔識新歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e500edf88d69dcadff67f7c097e7a6abf68c4af9","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神奇之旅都幾好聽</blockquote><br />\n許廷鏗17年轉咗新公司 真係恭喜佢啊