68c4af9","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神奇之旅都幾好聽</blockquote><br />\n許廷鏗17年轉咗新公司 真係恭喜佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試多咗好多唔同新嘢<br />\n雖然有啲新嘗試可能令佢敗露咗少少佢演繹上嘅限制，未必首首歌嘅曲風都駕馭得好好，會令我覺得有啲歌比其他人唱會更精彩<br />\n但肯跳出框框 隻碟整體又做得唔錯 係抵讚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻碟我暫時最鍾意 大雄胖虎綜合症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"許廷鏗隻碟做得唔錯<br />\n甩左星前班底真係好好多<br />\n只可惜佢vocal 唱得太差<br />\n影響左隻碟質素<br />\n麻煩佢真係要搞搞佢唱功"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"堆班底真係不得了<br />\n硬係覺得佢嘥咗個班底，如果啲歌俾其他人唱一定仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點都好，佢本身都算係唱得之人，離開星夢點都係件好事黎，繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0543b380b6e6a27eafe9069fda93a37ba093978f","tid":523793,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"Gem victoria"},{"pid":"d5f10ac44071d964fd60539c088ff95e668e3eb7","tid":523793,"uid":29237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0100b7cdb715263d229271242906aab3695abfb2","tid":523793,"uid":50676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"神奇之旅都幾好聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"我都幾鍾意神奇之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7cbda174857578e2474185d718eaab6149108d","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家個堆新秀真係無乜人識 唔入呢個POST都唔知有咩歌 廣東歌依家係唔係冇老細肯宣傳 除左上CCTVB個堆/電台 唔睇CCTVB同電台等同唔識新歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實打開電視都唔會識到好多歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncctvb同各大唱片公司不和，基本上都係死播爛播星夢劇集歌加英皇啲歌，啲音樂節目又越做越垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但近三兩年嗰堆劇集歌又唔知點解會hit得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明我以為cctvb影響力應該越來越細 <br />\nviutv又冇乜擺資源落音樂節目，主要淨係同環球合作&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n電台 後生生又好少會聽<br />\n<br />\n雖然網上好似好多平台可以宣傳，但某程度網上宣傳就係同緊全世界競爭，冇留意開嘅人都未必會接觸到"},{"pid":"58f5995ab24de4602139f8be12bcee354993648f","tid":523793,"uid":23919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"樓主揀嗰啲又幾啱我心水<br />\n<br />\n不過鐘舒漫我比較鐘意小碎步多啲"},{"pid":"4fcc11733bb9bb85ab5a54075f75d13d86e9549d","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實<br />\n要介紹就應該介紹2018既新廣東歌俾多d人認識<br />\n仲介紹17做咩</blockquote><br />\n18年開始咗冇耐唔係好多歌 仲要唔係隻隻都好聽又啱聽&hellip; <br />\n我又唔想開個po淨係講三幾首歌 好打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係話keep住講新歌嗰類，又同隔籬 香港流行音樂討論 個po撞撞地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n17年socalled叫啱啱派哂樂壇成績表<br />\n有啲歌係高質而我又鍾意嘅 但又冇獎攞，所以想推推嗰啲歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(年年都有人話唔識啲新人 所以推下佢地好嘅作品；<br />\n有啲之前做得霉霉地 17年有驚喜 值得讓人比多次機會嘅歌手 又想推下佢地啲歌；<br />\n有啲名不經傳嘅歌手17年有好歌 值得推比更多人識；<br />\n仲有啲underrated嘅滄海遺珠，同埋我喜歡嘅歌 都想推下)<br />\n當然亦想大家又介紹下鍾意咩歌 等我又留意下 唔洗走寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ace7a93c6bb0086442029e02ea9e7146d4aa3","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gem victoria</blockquote><br />\n咁耐冇唱廣東歌 一唱就係依類歌舞昇平歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由佢把口唱咩七百萬人團結和諧  真係有夠嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[black]你條專同連登仔唱反調嘅假膠真係好煩&hellip;[/black]"},{"pid":"85ffc5e37785766a5283884832229f83db75434c","tid":523793,"uid":34075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"07befe3567aad4d3d743898522f3fc71d40770dd","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"冇人講下鍾意咩舊年嘅歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"Robynn and Kendy - 急救中<br />\nGin Lee - 空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433d16abf08663d8824a257f065c0e11c67b18cd","tid":523793,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85ffc5e37785766a5283884832229f83db75434c","tid":523793,"uid":34075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"07befe3567aad4d3d743898522f3fc71d40770dd","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"冇人講下鍾意咩舊年嘅歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"Robynn and Kendy - 急救中<br />\nGin Lee - 空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:21:38.000Z","msg":"仲有 林奕匡 - 是日休息絕不工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faafa29b31a5c4cc68353d484f76b5673c156bfe","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主揀嗰啲又幾啱我心水<br />\n<br />\n不過鐘舒漫我比較鐘意小碎步多啲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我都覺得小碎步啱聽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一開始自己定咗想要揀三台都冇獎嘅歌<br />\n但數17年又覺得一定要數到鍾舒漫，啲歌造得好有個人風格又好出色<br />\n而且be water my friend亦係一首高質 值得推介嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d33dfc861f797092c36110eb2548d712f13c455","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇人講下鍾意咩舊年嘅歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Robynn and Kendy - 急救中<br />\nGin Lee - 空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>仲有 林奕匡 - 是日休息絕不工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nr&amp;k 17年狀態大勇 好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負攝石 無敵 shout n cry 急救中 世界對我們 首首都好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個獎都冇真係r哂頭 (我諗如果環球去新城嘅話 佢地應該起碼有個組合獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\ngin lee 17年我始終鍾意佢啲快歌多啲<br />\n隨風而來隨風而去 曌 今朝有酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然幾首慢歌都係水準之作<br />\n整體上 成隻碟好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林奕匡 17年又係好多好歌<br />\n第一個早晨 難得一遇 查無此字 有淚多好 是日休息絕不工作 首首都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係年尾嗰隻草原差少小<br />\nbtw 可唔可以唔好隻隻歌都比陳詠謙填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bfe2ec6398607b2adc5fba7c78779c8aa5fe0a","tid":523793,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0ace7a93c6bb0086442029e02ea9e7146d4aa3","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gem victoria</blockquote><br />\n咁耐冇唱廣東歌 一唱就係依類歌舞昇平歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由佢把口唱咩七百萬人團結和諧  真係有夠嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[black]你條專同連登仔唱反調嘅假膠真係好煩&hellip;[/black]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"盲反到 都唔知