oji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"未打完<br />\n急救中個mv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87baa5aca9ef9d09c1c9aa5d960c82a8604286ab","tid":523793,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇人講下鍾意咩舊年嘅歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Robynn and Kendy - 急救中<br />\nGin Lee - 空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>仲有 林奕匡 - 是日休息絕不工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nr&amp;k 17年狀態大勇 好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負攝石 無敵 shout n cry 急救中 世界對我們 首首都好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個獎都冇真係r哂頭 (我諗如果環球去新城嘅話 佢地應該起碼有個組合獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\ngin lee 17年我始終鍾意佢啲快歌多啲<br />\n隨風而來隨風而去 曌 今朝有酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然幾首慢歌都係水準之作<br />\n整體上 成隻碟好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林奕匡 17年又係好多好歌<br />\n第一個早晨 難得一遇 查無此字 有淚多好 是日休息絕不工作 首首都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係年尾嗰隻草原差少小<br />\nbtw 可唔可以唔好隻隻歌都比陳詠謙填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Robynn and Kendy好似未係叱咤扲過獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其他嗰三個就算啦.....</span></span><br />\n<br />\nGin Lee 今年呢隻碟真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呢兩隻都係叱咤女銀<br />\n<br />\n林奕匡最正始終都係 是日休息絕不工作 呢頖類嘅歌真係唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陳詠謙填得都唔係算好差吖 起碼佢有d歌都幾正 e.g.關楚耀首死亡之吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>同意Gin Lee隻碟好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實覺得仲高質過Janice果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過惟一唔好就係空姐接住落和每天講再見真係悶到訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  另外Gin Lee character仲係唔夠強 唔該環球係呢方面諗諗佢 至於Janice全年最出色都只係I Don&rsquo;t Know I Don&rsquo;t Care 隻碟入面穿花蝴蝶同一格格可聽性都高 至於其他就一律k歌格 不過都未必係壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意 作為一隻碟 gin lee嗰隻高質啲 完整性高啲<br />\n衛蘭當初出穿花蝴蝶嗰時 真係有蛻變feel 以為佢揾啱方向 對佢好大期望 <span style=\"color: navy;\">(就算唔鍾意陳詠謙都覺得份詞ok)</span> <br />\n點知依兩年比我感覺都仲有好似摸索階段咁 <br />\n出咗道咁多年仲係咁 真係有啲失望<br />\n<br />\ngin lee個問題都係差唔多 不過佢就似係自己本身有諗法 而且成熟嘅，但公司要捧佢想平衡市場因素嗰啲嘢，plug歌太保守<br />\n<br />\n當然其實佢兩個啲歌唔係唔正嘅<br />\n只係對佢地有期望，覺得佢地可以更上一層樓"}]}